<template>
  <NoteView v-for="note of this.notes" :key="note.id" :note="note"></NoteView>
</template>

<script>
import NoteView from "./NoteView.vue"

export default {
  name: 'NotesContainer',
  props: {
  },
  components: {
    NoteView,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      notes: [
        {
          id: 0,
          timestamp: "12:34",
          contents: "Hello World",
        },
        {
          id: 1,
          timestamp: "12:35",
          contents: "Goodbye World",
        }
      ],
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style scoped>
:nth-child(odd) {
  background: #F4FAFF;
}
</style>
